mixin search-modal
  .search-modal
    .container
      .search-modal__inner
        .search-modal__container
          .search-modal__close
            +close-svg('search-modal__close-button')
          form.search-modal__form(action="#")
            input.search-modal__input(type="text" name='request' id='search-modal-input')
            label.search-modal__label(for='search-modal-input')
              |Что вы хотите найти?
            button.search-modal__submit(type="submit")
              |поиск